pull_request.title: Added testing of SHA-3 AVX2 implementations
CMake refactoring.
pull_request.body:
1. Overhauled the propagation of compiler flags

2. Added `Dependency` CMake build type and the `LIBOQS_BUILD_TYPE` variable. 

`LIBOQS_BUILD_TYPE`, when specified, is assigned to `CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE`, and can be set in the CMakeLists.txt build files of other projects that use liboqs as a dependency. 

When `CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE` is `Dependency`, only `liboqs` is built, and the `gen_docs`, `prettyprint`, and `run_tests` targets (along with any corresponding build artifacts) are excluded. Besides reducing build time, this also ensures that a name collision will not occur if, for example, there is a `run_tests` target in the parent project using liboqs.

3. Removed src/common/CMakeLists.txt and src/crypto/CMakeLists.txt
